casebody.data:
Thursday, October 12, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

95-2032. State v. Raymundo.

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay of execution be, and hereby is, denied, effective October 11, 1995.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas and Resnick, JJ., dissent.
